o What Extent is Freedom of Speech Influenced by Power, Control, and Fear?<br />\n<br />\n我會首先講what is freedom of speech, why is it important, 然後分別用例子講power, control同fear有幾大程度會影響freedom of speech, 然後可能再排程度大至細咁樣<br />\n<br />\nstructure 大致上有無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解要排大細?<br />\n題目又無叫你排, 有D多餘 又唔係重點<br />\nPOWER--&gt;你既見解 人地既見解, QUOTATION, 例子 夠你寫800字<br />\n有必要先3樣溝起黎用一個例子講 <br />\n再唔夠字就引用下PSYCHOLOGY / 你讚果科 既野<br />\n3000字唔難寫 愈少字愈難寫呀"},{"pid":"6b9daa74034324ace66ed42c4157dab57c1971d9","tid":41764,"uid":16949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"你漏左counter statement"},{"pid":"c4683c7f5fd24cee2033ccf83b8e011f9b55b013","tid":41764,"uid":6386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>how to apply to issue</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啫係寫出嚟點表達既問題?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係你啲theory要應用落啲issue到<br />\n<br />\n解釋個現象<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"9d3d4a969e0c9671838cf19860dbdd41ec9f8b2d","tid":41764,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"要有logic"},{"pid":"e24280e2cd013f642b6d261507a0abcf36ca322f","tid":41764,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>For example:<br />\nTo What Extent is Freedom of Speech Influenced by Power, Control, and Fear?<br />\n<br />\n我會首先講what is freedom of speech, why is it important, 然後分別用例子講power, control同fear有幾大程度會影響freedom of speech, 然後可能再排程度大至細咁樣<br />\n<br />\nstructure 大致上有無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解要排大細?<br />\n題目又無叫你排, 有D多餘 又唔係重點<br />\nPOWER--&amp;gt;你既見解 人地既見解, QUOTATION, 例子 夠你寫800字<br />\n有必要先3樣溝起黎用一個例子講 <br />\n再唔夠字就引用下PSYCHOLOGY / 你讚果科 既野<br />\n3000字唔難寫 愈少字愈難寫呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我想問 intro 寫 this essay will examine 乜乜乜咁樣寫係咪唔係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學寫essay老師會叫咁樣寫但我發覺大學咁寫好似有啲怪 但又唔知應該點寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c50cfae20490c96aa5065387bd0564aaf0b1d4","tid":41764,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你漏左counter statement</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係喎唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}